content.query:
SELECT TOP 100 [koeredoegn]
    ,[tog_nr]
    --,[vogntur_start_station_UIC]
    ,[vogntur_start_station_fork]
    --,[vogntur_end_station_UIC]
    ,[vogntur_end_station_fork]
    ,[vogntur_start_tid]
    ,[vogntur_end_tid]
    ,[vogntur_distance]
    --,[station_aktuel_UIC]
    ,[station_aktuel_fork]
    ,[station_sekvens]
    ,tog_sekvens
    ,[ank_tid]
    ,[afg_tid]
    ,[station_forrige]
    ,[station_naeste]
    ,[statmlm_next_distance]
    ,[stop_type]
    ,[spor]
    ,[tog_kategori]
    ,[Koereplan72timer]
    ,[saet_nr]
    ,[litra_type]
    ,[litra_nr]
    ,[trip_type]
    ,[pre_tog_nr]
    ,[pre_koeredoegn]
    ,[pre_ank_tid]
    ,[pre_ank_timestamp]
    ,[post_tog_nr]
    ,[post_koeredoegn]
    ,[post_afg_tid]
    ,[post_afg_timestamp]
FROM [atlas-srvless-sql-dev].[IVU].[Protal_DM]
WHERE tog_nr = 125
AND litra_nr = 5095
ORDER BY koeredoegn, tog_nr, vogntur_start_tid, station_sekvens, litra_nr, saet_nr
